{"tid":1551106,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國防長關注香港問題　促中國保持克制以對話解決分歧","createTime":"2019-09-07T23:51:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-08T03:15:15.000Z","uid":50457,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b7e1912df42141c6d8a9a1a147805f614b38cdd5","tid":1551106,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T23:51:49.000Z","msg":"美國國防部長埃斯珀表示，關注香港目前的情況，敦促中國在香港問題上保持克制，不要採取行動，而是坐下來與示威者透過對話，解決分歧，認為這是最好的發展方向。<br />\n<br />\n埃斯帕在法國巴黎與法國國防部長帕利舉行聯合記者會，表示美國支持全球所有人享有自由，和平集會和表達對政府的關注。他又在記者會上，警告歐洲國家不要過分依賴中國投資，表示一個國家對中國貿易投資越來越依賴，一旦他們沒有按北京的意願行事，會變得更容易受到脅迫和報復，認為所有國家在有關對華關係問題上作出明智的決策，是至關重要的。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479415-20190908.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479415-20190908.htm&d=N8yyMuQB0XA0Wgs8sIkprlJiVKGJ8LWvq%2BeQg4NrPGo%3D&h=f560ac7a\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1479415-20190908.htm&h=67b99872\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1479415-20190908.htm</a>"},{"pid":"618287951f2a48da4444c06b13a30620f0bebe9c","tid":1551106,"uid":93986,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:15:56.000Z","msg":"中國同普世價值觀相差太大，根本唔應該俾佢地涉足太多"},{"pid":"faf541c545d59278b177e3ea234767ae2bf15af0","tid":1551106,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3aa04aeb2031c4c206b73e759543a88773e21027","tid":1551106,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-08T00:56:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e5b4aa8fa43a7399405c4ac8a11163b4708dbf8","tid":1551106,"uid":55913,"like":1,"disli